The [[Bayer designation]] '''Xi Capricorni''' (ξ Cap, ξ Capricorni) is shared by two [[star system]]s, in the [[constellation]] [[Capricornus]]: * [[Xi1 Capricorni|ξ¹ Capricorni]] * [[Xi2 Capricorni|ξ² Capricorni]], being the brighter of the two, often simply called ξ Capricorni They are separated by 0.25° in the sky.
